contributionDescription:
I’m brand new to OP but I’m digging In. I’ve helped three friends make accounts already and plan on spreading the word in a few groups I’m in on fbook and X. 
This is nothing new for me. I’ve been a helper for asking as I can remember especially in the crypto scene. 
I’ve helped onboard tons of people onto a bunch of sites. 
It’s literally what I do and it makes me feel good seeing people flourish from alittle help from their friends!
impactDescription:
Like I said in the previous description, I’m brand new to OP but this is nothing new for me. I’ve been helping to onboard users two sites that I find interesting and useful for years and I have no plans on stopping.
